{"tid":1404262,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"無論係勇武定和理非，出得黎既都同我睇左佢！","createTime":"2019-08-04T03:39:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T06:12:46.000Z","uid":277273,"like":54,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"df0bcb87d870494540df301b6a7a0305dff9e5c6","tid":1404262,"uid":277273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T03:39:36.000Z","msg":"工作關係成日有機會喺前線，近來見住夢孩喺上環等地比人拉，好撚心痛。<br />\n唔排除有夢孩做左最壞打算，但亦見到有啲被捕時係真心好驚、覺得好突然， <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">完全無諗過係自己被捕</span></strong></span>！<br />\n<br />\n唔係讚狗，但狗有四隻腳，真係跑得好撚快，一要捉人，前排（甚至二、三排）的夢孩係真係會跑唔切而被捕。<br />\n<br />\n唔該大家，我唔係烏鴉口，咀咒你地，但<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>上得黎前線，可唔可以有被捕的心理準備，最基本寫定被捕支援喺手</strong></span></span>（只喺手機唔夠，你點知到時比唔比你用自己電話），唔好以為自己會無事！就乜都無準備！！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果真係咁不幸，無寫到被捕支援電話喺手，到真係被捕時，就算現場無社工（啲狗會推開社工） 只要現場有啲記者甚至係觀察員，都有機會可以幫到你，唔該<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>被禁喺地下時，要不斷大叫自己個名</strong></span></span>！ （記者佢地本身角色中立，唔可以主動出聲問你名，但<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">如果被動地聽到你的求救，就有機會幫到你！</span></span>）<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>要全名好重要，如果唔係就算有義務律師想去警署幫你，如果無你個全名，狗係唔會比律師見你嫁！！！</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n8.4旺角拉人好明顯同之前唔同，一拉完人五分鐘內就上警車，社工黎到時都已經搵唔到被捕者。<br />\n<br />\n所以，記住！要大叫自己個名！！（如果你真係擔心叫完名會上哂live，被秋後算帳的話，就唔該你寫定被捕支援電話喺手啦！！ )<br />\n<br />\n至於被捕後要做咩回應，好多post 有講，就唔重複。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: green;\">我無嘢講。<br />\n我要見律師。<br />\n我要去醫院。</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"f09de6197154582e52987dd824555b8f005819f0","tid":1404262,"uid":277273,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T03:40:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7sCqJuO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7sCqJuO.png&h=5a466b79&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/syj1gPP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fsyj1gPP.png&h=bc82e138&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1eb0ae75a775ba4bd4be89e96da391868eea5420","tid":1404262,"uid":277273,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T03:42:46.000Z","msg":"對不起 728我被捕了 【親身整合分享】<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1392448\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1392448</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b20b912f2703596e17e3178c7651971ad6e8be03","tid":1404262,"uid":230870,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T03:45:04.000Z","msg":"皇天擊殺，香港警察<br />\n中共倒台，光復香港<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d31ad9b77fcc935a8fb4a91209735d6d5997a506","tid":1404262,"uid":277273,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T03:47:42.000Z","msg":"被捕人士入來看<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1283539\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1283539</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n728被捕手足既心聲[代po]<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1394929\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1394929</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n[整合版] 被捕人仕須知<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1189807\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1189807</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"af332853c6fc39f2a9a5debafd92ba1b6f5f8269","tid":1404262,"uid":277273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T03:49:53.000Z","msg":"我無嘢講"},{"pid":"194abe2b0f9b304ae1b7e6c5e4a2a4a38d9709a2","tid":1404262,"uid":277273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T03:50:17.000Z","msg":"我無嘢講"},{"pid":"52c829e086f483006cfe7379046b8727323cf22a","tid":1404262,"uid":277273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T03:50:57.000Z","msg":"我要見律師"},{"pid":"b6a6321561653c64dd5d8904a58dc1d83b20036d","tid":1404262,"uid":277273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T03:51:28.000Z","msg":"我要去醫院"},{"pid":"2832fc849add63ff1cc716326b71ce89b19443d2","tid":1404262,"uid":277273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T03:52:11.000Z","msg":"如果你，或你的朋友，在衝突中受傷、被捕，而需要法律及醫療支援的話，請立即聯絡我們了解詳情。<br />\n<br />\n請記得，大家若果被捕，是有權打給律師的。若擔心屆時未能打電話，建議你將自己的：<br />\n中英文全名、<br />\n身份證號碼、<br />\n年齡、<br />\n聯絡電話<br />\n等資料，預先交託給可靠的朋友，朋友一旦發現你被捕，就可以代你聯絡律師。<br />\n<br />\n各位保重。<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n反送中傷者被捕者人道支援基金：<br />\n9845 6641 （致電/sms）<br />\n<br />\n被捕支援<br />\n<br />\n民權觀察 <br />\n9463 2945（tg/sms/whatsapp）<br />\n民陣 <br />\n6549 9452 (whatsapp/telegram/sms)<br />\n伍展邦律師 <br />\n@hksup（tg) / 5690 2877（whatsapp） / 2608 1400<br />\n<br />\n韋智達律師 9167 7091<br />\n<br />\n星火同盟 （fb inbox）<br />\n<br />\n本土民主前線 <br />\n5934 5588 (whatsapp/sms) @Hkibackup （tg)<br />\n<br />\n港大 9139 0589<br />\n中大 9443 3459<br />\n科大 6019 6339 / 2335 1732 / 2335 5672<br />\n浸大 6110 3860<br />\n城大 9545 4172 / 3442 5570<br />\n理大 6800 0560 / 2766 7025 / 6253 2359<br />\n教大 5108 3519<br />\n演藝 6679 0772 / 9464 5078<br />\n<br />\n如見抗爭者被捕，請大家連同以下資料，聯絡上述單位：<br />\n1. 被捕者中文姓名<br />\n2. 被捕者英文姓名<br />\n3. 被捕者身份證號碼<br />\n4. 被捕者乘坐之警車號碼 / 所在警署"},{"pid":"86842396d0dcb286200024c7261870b9e97618be","tid":1404262,"uid":277273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T03:53:17.000Z","msg":"我無嘢講"},{"pid":"0ee5767853204465e8402205b83611c1fdc88fed","tid":1404262,"uid":277273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T03:54:37.000Z","msg":"我要見律師"},{"pid":"cff360c9d1e96eababca1994a3bc592cb386b939","tid":1404262,"uid":277273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T03:55:36.000Z","msg":"我要去醫院"},{"pid":"d2750d284fd2938a9a0cb0e4baf922328261fdff","tid":1404262,"uid":277273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T03:56:45.000Z","msg":"推啊"},{"pid":"e505c8a6bbe0a1ba8551563d0364e19e9065ac46","tid":1404262,"uid":277273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T04:04:35.000Z","msg":"我無補充"},{"pid":"3168e71ac49560c24b4ec3d65f38a8f27bc30907","tid":1404262,"uid":277273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T04:10:05.000Z","msg":"我無嘢講"},{"pid":"905466e8b44cbc18f6e23db61f3edbd72d1c40aa","tid":1404262,"uid":277273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T04:36:04.000Z","msg":"＜關於受傷和暴動罪＞<br />\n<br />\n我是於6月12日金鐘示威活動中眼睛受槍傷、被警方以暴動罪拘捕的一名教師。受傷至今，我遵從不同的法律及專業意見，婉拒了大部分的傳媒訪問，但仍有很多朋友和市民對我的情況表示關注。最近更有40多名市民被控暴動罪。我能感受被控者的茫然不安。<br />\n<br />\n本文載有我對一些問題和評論的回應，以及我對暴動罪的認識，希望可以一次過解釋我的情況和看法，並給予同路人參考。<br />\n<br />\n詳細自己睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/100004203397436/posts/1399272470222853?s=506220323&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F100004203397436%2Fposts%2F1399272470222853%3Fs%3D506220323%26sfns%3Dmo&d=Yc7MVk%2FjSym3Ma7OIK9USA5Iyec62GFiithg4eFnous%3D&h=2bea5786\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/100004203397436/posts/1399272470222853?s=506220323&amp;sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"981feb3bef7650c751b7630d8cd78c4b02898d71","tid":1404262,"uid":277273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T04:40:37.000Z","msg":"加陣警察郁啲就告暴動罪，<br />\n而暴動罪其實好易入罪<br />\n<br />\n你出現喺暴動現場已經算係，所以唔該大家真係做好最壞的準備！！"},{"pid":"7c3bf341d6d1a212592e82b0e63e24f50053bfec","tid":1404262,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T04:55:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f8e5fbddb746fc7b794fd581bbe7a3d84be98cc","tid":1404262,"uid":203713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T04:55:58.000Z","msg":"入黎救義士<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1404076\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1404076</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f34893151728c52147c7adf820d24214486ee586","tid":1404262,"uid":216390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T05:03:11.000Z","msg":"我無嘢講"},{"pid":"156e7910a91d610d0c05076401ace868dd374be4","tid":1404262,"uid":258055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T05:07:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a49cfe5336b76c1380e02b09b99ad67efbccdd97","tid":1404262,"uid":11382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T05:07:50.000Z","msg":"東區醫院有大量狗隻出現於A&amp;E<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1404524\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1404524</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"4edb177d6db176156363fde42c6cb88ace1de706","tid":1404262,"uid":40286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T05:08:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">係時候轉下玩法</span></span><br />\n<br />\n同狗打 對政府冇影響 <br />\n對真係揸權嘅土共更加冇影響<br />\n要一針見血 就要搵政權最著緊嘅野同佢玩 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">錢</span></span><br />\n<br />\n[不合作運動全面升級] 不論和理非/勇武，入一入嚟。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1403657\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1403657</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"3fbfd4247763afd3830148a0739768d65f41c356","tid":1404262,"uid":277273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T05:08:39.000Z","msg":"推"}]}